The app uses TikTok Login Kit to allow users to securely connect their TikTok account. After authentication, the app can access basic user information such as username and profile data.

The Content Posting API is used to allow users to upload videos to their TikTok account. Users can generate video content externally and then publish it through the platform.

The app workflow is simple:
1. The user opens the website.
2. The user logs in using their TikTok account.
3. The user creates or selects a video.
